metadata.name: Venus in Pisces
metadata.description:
Undress to the nakedness of love.

Venus in Pisces.
Love in exaltation.
A force that invades just like the ocean and transcends everything.

A hopeless romantic, she seeks only what satisfies her deepest fantasies. She is enchanted by ethereal love, she longs for sacred connections, and to experience love like a deep state of meditation.

But she can get lost in the sea of idealization as well.

Venus in her exaltation operates in her highest expression. If thereâ€™s any part of you not yet receptive to love, Venus in Pisces is bringing the healing, the forgiveness, and is supporting you to soften up. 


Insights: Astro By Nala
Artwork: Midnight Moon Visuals
